			<fdd:keyword>Indeo</fdd:keyword>
		</fdd:keywords>
		<fdd:description>File format with an Indeo video bitstream with other data chunks, e.g., audio, in an AVI wrapper. Indeo versions 3.1 and 3.2 employ vector quantization; versions 4 and 5 use forms of wavelet compression.</fdd:description>
		<fdd:shortDescription>File format that wraps an Indeo video bitstream with other data chunks, e.g., audio, in an AVI wrapper. </fdd:shortDescription>
		<fdd:productionPhase>Generally a final-state format for enduser delivery. </fdd:productionPhase>
